{"tid":2218314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗窮撚唔好生仔之外，有遺傳病都唔好生仔","createTime":"2020-09-26T06:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T07:14:19.000Z","uid":113516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c2215cd64521ea07489fd65f7675bf1a7b9b9e49","tid":2218314,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:24:28.000Z","msg":"唔好話我口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但自己本身有事就唔應該遺禍俾下一代啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到自己咁辛苦做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說，屋企人有個耶撚朋友，佢自己有遺傳病 (唔記得係邊種，但經常要出入醫院check血，有時要住院觀察)<br />\n<br />\n早幾年生咗個小朋友出嚟，依家K3，個小朋友都係一樣有事<br />\ne.g. 仲係bb嗰陣都已經身體差，長期食完嘢會嘔返出嚟，唔肯瞓，唔知幾時開始diagnose咗有自閉症<br />\n<br />\n最近呢個老母又因為有事要入醫院觀察，佢老公又返夜班睇唔到小朋友，佢屋企又冇人幫手照顧小朋友 (好似同家人炒大鑊) <br />\n<br />\nbtw 我都唔知係咪關佢宗教信仰事，堅持一定要有下一代，但一句講哂呢個老母真係好自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小朋友又身體差又有自閉症都唔知點算"},{"pid":"ee02d0280f5dff739d89f46b099799a5319d7500","tid":2218314,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個小朋友好慘"},{"pid":"54fa9b016f760c39a0e150e9647aad3c6747f8df","tid":2218314,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"仲有樣衰嗰啲，咪出嚟獻世"},{"pid":"5957e140ad98a6da101e67c4ffa022bfc74245e0","tid":2218314,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54fa9b016f760c39a0e150e9647aad3c6747f8df","tid":2218314,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"仲有樣衰嗰啲，咪出嚟獻世"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea42b3f8b2b8b9675dc2aee0a4883f00cbf4d71","tid":2218314,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"生命黎<br />\n唔通你個frd落咗個仔咩"},{"pid":"2acf4ce4cbad1c2e7e9204d7b7791dc8dd1aad9f","tid":2218314,"uid":325200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:36:05.000Z","msg":"我遺傳好撚咸濕<br />\n生左個仔出黎之前佢家陣8歲<br />\n仲日日喊「媽咪飲奶」<br />\n仲要一路劣條J一路飲<br />\n搞撚到我又嬲但係又想啜埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6725655b7d65f19c72def40b57be962b85f7977b","tid":2218314,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ea42b3f8b2b8b9675dc2aee0a4883f00cbf4d71","tid":2218314,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"生命黎<br />\n唔通你個frd落咗個仔咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"但重點係，自己知自己有病<br />\n生仔前都徵詢下醫生意見，究竟自己適唔適估生小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f08a7a7c2eed0a9c6172762e06ce8d12ad6406","tid":2218314,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6725655b7d65f19c72def40b57be962b85f7977b","tid":2218314,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ea42b3f8b2b8b9675dc2aee0a4883f00cbf4d71","tid":2218314,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"生命黎<br />\n唔通你個frd落咗個仔咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"但重點係，自己知自己有病<br />\n生仔前都徵詢下醫生意見，究竟自己適唔適估生小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:39:33.000Z","msg":"適唔適<span class=\"red\">合</span>*"},{"pid":"64d714c620fa17cf192889a95287eea086a8a136","tid":2218314,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6725655b7d65f19c72def40b57be962b85f7977b","tid":2218314,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ea42b3f8b2b8b9675dc2aee0a4883f00cbf4d71","tid":2218314,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"生命黎<